1.1               ST reference
The ST has the revision v4.0 and is dated 2020-10-15. The title of this document IFX_CCI_00002Dh,
IFX_CCI_000039h, IFX_CCI_00003Ah, IFX_CCI_000044h, IFX_CCI_000045h, IFX_CCI_000046h, IFX_CCI_000047h,
